Package com.example.eventlottery.data

Interface ProfileRepository

All Known Implementing Classes:
FirebaseProfileRepository, MockProfileRepository
public interface ProfileRepository
Repository interface for managing user profiles and authentication. Login/registration is based solely on deviceID for auto-detected authentication.
